reviewText: Very nice dvd. You can really get a sense of the design differences between houses.
Great view of some great jewelry houses. Lot's of information for a jewelry designer.
It is a great DVD on the history of the famous jewelry designers of our times. Exactly what I was looking for and will be a treasure to watch over and over.
love it!  will use this in my class when it teach gemology. wonderful to add to my collection for teach
